                    <span class="duration">Feb 2025 - March 2025</span>
                </div>
                <p class="tech-stack"><em>Python, Scikit-learn, Apriori, Random Forest</em></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Built a breast cancer classification system integrating GANs for synthetic data generation with SMOTETomek for addressing dataset imbalance issues, enabling more accurate predictions for minority class cases.</li>
                    <li>Applied the Apriori algorithm to uncover significant association rules between patient attributes and cancer recurrence, identifying critical patterns distinguishing recurrent and non-recurrent cases.</li>
                    <li>The model attained outstanding performance metrics, including 85% precision, 85% recall, and 91% ROC-AUC score, highlighting its robust predictive abilities for both cancer detection and recurrence.</li>
                </ul>
