            <div class="project-item">
                <div class="project-header">
                    <h3>LangChain RAG for Educational Content Analysis</h3>
                    <span class="duration">Jan 2025 – March 2025</span>
                </div>
                <p class="tech-stack"><em>Python, LangChain, LLMs</em></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>An advanced AI-powered question analysis system was formulated, utilizing Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) and Large Language Models to process and categorize educational content from PDF files accurately.</li>
                    <li>A comprehensive classification framework was implemented to systematically sort questions into five specific categories: one-word answers, true/false, multiple-choice, short-answer, and long-answer formats.</li>
                    <li>A Python-based solution was created, incorporating external knowledge retrieval methods to facilitate efficient processing of educational content.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="project-item">
                <div class="project-header">
                    <h3>Complex Frame DNA Video Steganography</h3>
                    <span class="duration">Feb 2024 – May 2024</span>
                </div>
                <p class="tech-stack"><em>Python, DNA Encoding, Caesar Cipher</em></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Developed a novel method for video steganography by integrating DNA-based data embedding with strategic frame selection, enabling advanced data concealment techniques.</li>
                    <li>Enhanced data protection by creating and embedding artificial DNA sequences into specific intricate frames, ensuring secure data transfer over the internet with minimal detectability.</li>
                    <li>Applied advanced encryption and steganographic techniques to protect sensitive information from unauthorized access, implementing multi-layered security protocols.</li>
                    <li>The average Peak Signal to Noise Ratio value secured was 95.25, and the Mean Square Error value was 1.4 × 10⁻⁶.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
